---

The Real Problem

You build an app on your laptop 

But…

How does it reach the user?

The DevOps Solution

Simple but powerful idea:

Developers + Operations work together 

---

--> Modern DevOps Flow:

Developer
   ↓
Write Code
   ↓
Push to Git
   ↓
CI/CD Pipeline 
   ↓
Build → Test → Deploy
   ↓
Cloud Server 
   ↓
Users get updates instantly 

